make sure that your ports are still forwarded? uhmmm if ur server wasnt up for long it could have came off of the server status list if u had it on one. make sure u have internet conection and open up your no-ip.duc and see if u still are using the same no-ip that u were using before? also. when your portforwarding make sure u double check the ip that ur using.
